        "message": "Patch Set 6: Verified+1\n\nBuild Successful \n\nhttps://jenkins.onap.org/job/rtdv3-global-verify-master/16700/ : SUCCESS\n\nLogs: https://logs.onap.org/production/vex-yul-ecomp-jenkins-1/rtdv3-global-verify-master/16700\n\nhttps://jenkins.onap.org/job/sdc-integration-tests-master-verify-java/3051/ : SUCCESS\n\nLogs: https://logs.onap.org/production/vex-yul-ecomp-jenkins-1/sdc-integration-tests-master-verify-java/3051\n\nhttps://jenkins.onap.org/job/sdc-master-verify-java/10634/ : SUCCESS\n\nLogs: https://logs.onap.org/production/vex-yul-ecomp-jenkins-1/sdc-master-verify-java/10634",
